This python script checks target.com for iPad inventory.

Author: Ian Scott <ian@polpo.org>
https://github.com/polpo/ipad-target.py

Usage:
./ipad-target.py mode zip [dpci] [dpci]...

mode can be either 'print' to simply print the results, or 'email' to email
them. Currently the email address is hardcoded in the script.

zip is the zip code to search.

dpci is Target's stock identifier for the iPad you're looking for. You can
specify multiple dpcis, or none, which will cause the script to look for all
iPad models around the specified zip code.

List of DPCIs:
 057-10-2020: 16GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi - Black (MC705LL/A)
 057-10-2021: 16GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi - White (MD328LL/A)
 057-10-2022: 32GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi - Black (MC706LL/A)
 057-10-2023: 32GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi - White (MD329LL/A)
 057-10-2024: 64GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi - Black (MC707LL/A)
 057-10-2025: 64GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi - White (MD330LL/A)
 057-10-2026: 16GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for AT&T - Black (MD366LL/A)
 057-10-2027: 16GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for AT&T - White (MD369LL/A)
 057-10-2028: 32GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for AT&T - Black (MD367LL/A)
 057-10-2029: 32GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for AT&T - White (MD370LL/A)
 057-10-2030: 64GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for AT&T - Black (MD368LL/A)
 057-10-2031: 64GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for AT&T - White (MD371LL/A)
 057-10-2032: 16GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for Verizon - Black (MC733LL/A)
 057-10-2033: 16GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for Verizon - White (MD363LL/A)
 057-10-2034: 32GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for Verizon - Black (MC744LL/A)
 057-10-2036: 32GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for Verizon - White (MD364LL/A)
 057-10-2037: 64GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for Verizon - Black (MC756LL/A)
 057-10-2038: 64GB The new iPad with Wi-Fi + 4G for Verizon - White (MD365LL/A)

